    vellum_post_67.body = u"I've decided that I don't like pulling individual tweets into the blog as uniquely styled posts. For now, that behavior has been disabled. I've moved to a single weekly aggregate post including all the previous week's tweets. We'll see how that goes.\n\nSince individual tweets are no longer being pulled in, I've put a list of the most recent tweets down in the footer. Next to that you'll also find a new list of the week's most popular posts. Fancy!"
