    vellum_post_111 = Post()
    vellum_post_111.title = u'Repackaged Soap Bar'
    vellum_post_111.slug = u'repackaged-soap-bar'
    vellum_post_111.author = None
    vellum_post_111.markup = u'markdown'
    vellum_post_111.body = u'Here\'s another great idea that I gleaned from scanning the <a href="http://www.backpackinglight.com/cgi-bin/backpackinglight/forums/index.html?id=9sTyccSp:216.254.23.78">BackpackingLight Forums</a>: using the plastic container from an old <a href="http://www.rei.com/product/747197">bike tube patch kit</a> as a soap bar container.\n\nWhole soap bars tend to be far too large and heavy for any but the longest of travels. Cutting up a bar of soap to make it smaller is easier enough, but prior to this I had never come across a correctly sized container to package it in.\n\n<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/pigmonkey/3868770543/" title="Repackaged Soap Bar by Pig Monkey, on Flickr"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2569/3868770543_7b83e7a027.jpg" width="500" height="375" alt="Repackaged Soap Bar" /></a>\n\nThis container is perfect. It measures in at 3.25" x 1.75" x 0.9", weighs 2.5 oz when full, and <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/pigmonkey/3869553772/">holds about 1/3rd of a bar</a> of <a href="http://www.drbronner.com/DBMS/BAR.htm">Dr. Bronner\'s Bar Soap</a>. I wrap a rubber band around it for added security.'
    vellum_post_111.body_rendered = u'<p>Here&#8217;s another great idea that I gleaned from scanning the <a href="http://www.backpackinglight.com/cgi-bin/backpackinglight/forums/index.html?id=9sTyccSp:216.254.23.78">BackpackingLight Forums</a>: using the plastic container from an old <a href="http://www.rei.com/product/747197">bike tube patch kit</a> as a soap bar container.</p>\n<p>Whole soap bars tend to be far too large and heavy for any but the longest of travels. Cutting up a bar of soap to make it smaller is easier enough, but prior to this I had never come across a correctly sized container to package it in.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/pigmonkey/3868770543/" title="Repackaged Soap Bar by Pig Monkey, on Flickr"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2569/3868770543_7b83e7a027.jpg" width="500" height="375" alt="Repackaged Soap Bar" /></a></p>\n<p>This container is perfect. It measures in at 3.25&#8221; x 1.75&#8221; x 0.9&#8221;, weighs 2.5 oz when full, and <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/pigmonkey/3869553772/">holds about 1/3rd of a bar</a> of <a href="http://www.drbronner.com/DBMS/BAR.htm">Dr. Bronner&#8217;s Bar Soap</a>. I wrap a rubber band around it for added security.</p>'
