    vellum_post_155 = Post()
    vellum_post_155.title = u'Vagabonding'
    vellum_post_155.slug = u'vagabonding-2'
    vellum_post_155.author = None
    vellum_post_155.markup = u'markdown'
    vellum_post_155.body = u'<blockquote>Of the gladdest moments in human life, methinks, is the departure upon a distant journey into unknown lands. Shaking off with one mighty effort the fetters of Habit, the leaden weight of Routine, the cloak of many Cares and the slavery of Home, man feels once more happy. The blood flows with the fast circulation of childhood... Afresh dawns the morn of life...\n- Sir Richard F. Burton, Journal entry, December 2, 1856</blockquote>'
