    vellum_post_272 = Post()
    vellum_post_272.title = u'I Am So Confused'
    vellum_post_272.slug = u'i-am-so-confused'
    vellum_post_272.author = None
    vellum_post_272.markup = u'markdown'
    vellum_post_272.body = u'So I was sitting here, at work, doing work stuff, when a reminder popped up. "Work in 14 minutes". "Wait a second," I thought "I\'m already at work." I check the calendar. I\'m not supposed to be at work till 3. My (atomic) watch said it was 2:47. Time.gov agreed with it.\n\nI\'m supposed to be in class 2-3 -- but I went to that class. The professor was there, my friends were there.\n\nWas the entire class an hour early?\n\nWill I be late to my next class?\n\nWhat time is it?\n\nTune in next week...'
