    vellum_post_466 = Post()
    vellum_post_466.title = u'Mosquitos'
    vellum_post_466.slug = u'mosquitos'
    vellum_post_466.author = None
    vellum_post_466.markup = u'markdown'
    vellum_post_466.body = u'One can always depend upon Tamarack Song to have a different -- dare I say hollistic? -- view of things. Over at <a href="http://www.natureskills.com/index.html" >Nature Skills</a>, he has an <a href="http://natureskills.com/mosquito_bite_prevention.html" >article on Mosquito Bite Prevention</a>. Some of his more interesting advise is thus:\n<ul>\n<li>Don\'t smell funny and they won\'t bite you. Avoid perfumes, "smell like you belong". (Eat garlic to mask your breath.)</li>\n<li>Don\'t look like a clown and they won\'t be attracted to you. Natural, earth hue colors help you to blend in.</li>\n<li>Bask on oil. Mosquitos don\'t like to get their wings greasy.</li>\n<li>Enjoy a breeze. Mosquitos can only fly 8mph.</li>\n</ul>'
