    vellum_post_570 = Post()
    vellum_post_570.title = u'Basic Security Practices'
    vellum_post_570.slug = u'basic-security-practices'
    vellum_post_570.author = None
    vellum_post_570.markup = u'markdown'
    vellum_post_570.body = u'<a href="http://www.al.com/redstone/index.ssf?/base/news/1132827506165260.xml&coll=1" >http://www.al.com/redstone/index.ssf?/base/news/1132827506165260.xml&coll=1</a>\n<blockquote>As a government employee, you\'ve heard it all before * lock your computer screen, protect your computer password, shred unwanted government documents, be careful about what is discussed in unclassified phone calls and e-mails, and practice vigilance in all matters related to workplace security.</blockquote>\n\nGovernment employee? These are the bare essentials that any one who\'s in contact with technology for more than 10 minutes a month should practice. Of course, you\'d replace "shred unwanted government documents" with "shred everything but the newspaper", "unclassified phone calls and e-mails" with "anything that isn\'t encrypted with a 2048 bit key", and "workplace security" with "personal security".'
    vellum_post_570.body_rendered = u'<p><a href="http://www.al.com/redstone/index.ssf?/base/news/1132827506165260.xml&amp;coll=1">http://www.al.com/redstone/index.ssf?/base/news/1132827506165260.xml&coll;=1</a>\n<blockquote>As a government employee, you&#8217;ve heard it all before * lock your computer screen, protect your computer password, shred unwanted government documents, be careful about what is discussed in unclassified phone calls and e-mails, and practice vigilance in all matters related to workplace security.</blockquote></p>\n<p>Government employee? These are the bare essentials that any one who&#8217;s in contact with technology for more than 10 minutes a month should practice. Of course, you&#8217;d replace &#8220;shred unwanted government documents&#8221; with &#8220;shred everything but the newspaper&#8221;, &#8220;unclassified phone calls and e-mails&#8221; with &#8220;anything that isn&#8217;t encrypted with a 2048 bit key&#8221;, and &#8220;workplace security&#8221; with &#8220;personal security&#8221;.</p>'
