    vellum_post_743 = Post()
    vellum_post_743.title = u'Converter'
    vellum_post_743.slug = u'converter'
    vellum_post_743.author = None
    vellum_post_743.markup = u'markdown'
    vellum_post_743.body = u'After hearing them on <a href="http://distortedcircuitry.com/" >Distorted Circuitry</a>, I picked up a copy of <a href="http://www.ant-zen.com/converter/" >Converter</a>\'s <a href="http://www.ant-zen.com/act/act143.htm" >Expansion Pack</a> (act143.31 and act143.32) from <a href="http://strangefortune.com/" >Strange Fortune</a>. Instead of simply coming as a normal CD, as I expected, it ended up behind two mini-cds, four tracks each. Very odd. I\'m pretty sure it would be cheaper to go for one normal CD, not to mention I can\'t play these in any slot-loaded player (such as my car), but...it\'s unique, I guess.\nI recommend picking the album(s) up, if you\'re into to (heavy) industrial. It\'s good stuff.\nI also recommend <a href="http://strangefortune.com/" >Strange Fortune</a> if you\'re looking for some underground industrial. I\'m pleased with them.'
    vellum_post_743.body_rendered = u'<p>After hearing them on <a href="http://distortedcircuitry.com/">Distorted Circuitry</a>, I picked up a copy of <a href="http://www.ant-zen.com/converter/">Converter</a>&#8216;s <a href="http://www.ant-zen.com/act/act143.htm">Expansion Pack</a> (act143.31 and act143.32) from <a href="http://strangefortune.com/">Strange Fortune</a>. Instead of simply coming as a normal CD, as I expected, it ended up behind two mini-cds, four tracks each. Very odd. I&#8217;m pretty sure it would be cheaper to go for one normal CD, not to mention I can&#8217;t play these in any slot-loaded player (such as my car), but&#8230;it&#8217;s unique, I guess.\nI recommend picking the album(s) up, if you&#8217;re into to (heavy) industrial. It&#8217;s good stuff.\nI also recommend <a href="http://strangefortune.com/">Strange Fortune</a> if you&#8217;re looking for some underground industrial. I&#8217;m pleased with them.</p>'
