    vellum_post_844.author = None
    vellum_post_844.markup = u'markdown'
    vellum_post_844.body = u'I\'ve been surfing freenet a bit more. At first it was quite scary. We\'re talking like total anarchism here. In the real world. Not one of Emma Goldman\'s speeches.<br />\n<br />\nOther than that, my time is being consumed by <a href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/tg/detail/-/0060512806/qid=1047006694/sr=8-1/ref=sr_8_1/002-8034415-5332862?v=glance&s=books&n=507846" >Cryptonomicon</a>. Why the hell is Neal Stephenson writing novels when his cryptanalysis skills are equal to that of Bruce Schneier (yes, <a href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0471117099/qid=1047006821/sr=2-1/ref=sr_2_1/002-8034415-5332862" >that</a> Bruce Schneier). Really, Cryptonomicon is half William Gibson and half cryptography manual.<br />\nEverybody should go read it.'
